{"body":[{"content":"「字幕由 富睿字幕組 搬運」\n（禁止在B站宣傳漫遊相關内容，否則拉黑）","location":2,"from":0,"to":1.15},{"content":"「字幕由 富睿字幕組 搬運」\n（禁止在B站宣傳漫遊相關内容，否則拉黑）\n(開始製作全世界獨一無二的陶器) (旁白 芹澤優)","from":1.15,"location":2,"to":1.67},{"content":"終於要開始製作自己的作品啦\n(開始製作全世界獨一無二的陶器) (旁白 芹澤優)","from":1.67,"location":2,"to":5.13},{"content":"我們要製作全世界獨一無二的陶器了哦","from":5.58,"location":2,"to":9.43},{"content":"( 燒窯馬克杯聲優將製作全世界獨一無二的陶器！)\n(挑戰草圖繪製！作品會是何種造型…!?)\n( ♪閃耀☆安弗倫特《輪迴×轉世》)\n你的歌聲越是熾熱 （我為了你）","from":10.66,"location":2,"to":16.54},{"content":"( 燒窯馬克杯聲優將製作全世界獨一無二的陶器！)\n(挑戰草圖繪製！作品會是何種造型…!?)\n( ♪閃耀☆安弗倫特《輪迴×轉世》)\n彼此描繪的夢想便越來越絢爛 （轉世重生）","from":16.54,"location":2,"to":22.95},{"content":"無須特別的言語 只要相伴身側 僅僅如此…","from":22.95,"location":2,"to":32.37},{"content":"只要相伴身側 僅僅如此便好 心懷炙熱思念","from":32.52,"location":2,"to":41.44},{"content":"(燒窯的話也要馬克杯 燒窯的放學後)","from":41.52,"location":2,"to":42.5},{"content":"燒窯的放學後\n(燒窯的話也要馬克杯 燒窯的放學後)","from":42.5,"location":2,"to":43.76},{"content":"(燒窯的話也要馬克杯 燒窯的放學後)","from":43.76,"location":2,"to":45.07},{"content":"這次我們來到了離多治見站10分鐘車程的地方","from":45.93,"location":2,"to":49.98},{"content":"從開展體驗教室到販售陶藝用品\n(學習陶藝的必備工具！)","from":51.06,"location":2,"to":54.7},{"content":"在這家陶器之聲 與陶藝相關的東西應有盡有\n(學習陶藝的必備工具！)","from":54.7,"location":2,"to":58.89},{"content":"那事不宜遲 讓我們趕緊來看看陶藝用品區吧","from":59.93,"location":2,"to":64.18},{"content":"雖然統稱為陶藝用品 但種類卻十分繁多","from":65.89,"location":2,"to":69.76},{"content":"有削黏土的泥塑刮刀","from":70.21,"location":2,"to":72.31},{"content":"還有修整陶土形狀的木刮片等 多種多樣","from":72.57,"location":2,"to":76.82},{"content":"好多工具啊","from":77.38,"location":2,"to":78.25},{"content":"居然有這麼多種工具啊","from":78.25,"location":2,"to":79.21},{"content":"是啊","from":79.21,"location":2,"to":79.58},{"content":"太厲害了","from":79.58,"location":2,"to":80.45},{"content":"感覺有點像做甜品的工具","from":80.8,"location":2,"to":83.28},{"content":"是的 是有些類似","from":83.28,"location":2,"to":84.22},{"content":"的確很像","from":84.22,"location":2,"to":84.78},{"content":"原來如此啊","from":84.78,"location":2,"to":86.11},{"content":"這是什麼","from":86.39,"location":2,"to":87.21},{"content":"像拐杖一樣","from":87.45,"location":2,"to":88.29},{"content":"可以紓解肩膀酸痛的那種東西","from":88.29,"location":2,"to":89.74},{"content":"像癢癢撓一樣的那種","from":89.74,"location":2,"to":90.76},{"content":"像這樣用的話… 感覺能正好按到穴位","from":91.07,"location":2,"to":94.91},{"content":"不禁會讓人拿來這麼用","from":94.91,"location":2,"to":96.92},{"content":"的確會","from":96.92,"location":2,"to":97.45},{"content":"這到底是用來做什麼的","from":97.45,"location":2,"to":98.48},{"content":"這個嘛… 各位認為是用來做什麼的？","from":98.48,"location":2,"to":101.39},{"content":"猜謎了猜謎了","from":101.74,"location":2,"to":102.79},{"content":"我知道了我知道了","from":102.79,"location":2,"to":104.65},{"content":"最喜歡你了","from":105.82,"location":2,"to":106.47},{"content":"這…你把它拼成愛心了啊","from":107.15,"location":2,"to":108.63},{"content":"他笑了","from":109.42,"location":2,"to":110.16},{"content":"-角度也太刁鑽了 -謝謝你的喜歡 -角度刁鑽","from":110.28,"location":2,"to":112.3},{"content":"田中先生 最喜歡你了","from":112.84,"location":2,"to":114.5},{"content":"不是這麼用的","from":115.58,"location":2,"to":116.11},{"content":"被直截了當地回絕了","from":117.49,"location":2,"to":118.69},{"content":"「不是這麼用的」","from":118.91,"location":2,"to":119.66},{"content":"這也太難猜了","from":119.66,"location":2,"to":120.43},{"content":"我想到了 正經的","from":120.72,"location":2,"to":122.09},{"content":"是不是用來修齊底邊弧線的","from":122.91,"location":2,"to":125.2},{"content":"是的 那個…這回答基本正確","from":125.52,"location":2,"to":128.47},{"content":"太強了","from":129.12,"location":2,"to":129.53},{"content":"像壺啊 花瓶啊","from":129.53,"location":2,"to":131.01},{"content":"做這種手搆不到裡面的作品就要拿著它伸進去…","from":131.52,"location":2,"to":136.36},{"content":"這麼來調整形狀","from":136.41,"location":2,"to":137.61},{"content":"是這麼用的啊","from":137.62,"location":2,"to":138.97},{"content":"不是用手的啊","from":139.02,"location":2,"to":140.09},{"content":"接著令人在意的是這個工具","from":141.39,"location":2,"to":144.37},{"content":"這是…？","from":144.68,"location":2,"to":145.44},{"content":"上面寫著「刨子」","from":146.52,"location":2,"to":147.93},{"content":"是的","from":147.93,"location":2,"to":148.27},{"content":"印象中刨子一般都是用來削東西的吧","from":148.42,"location":2,"to":151.0},{"content":"是的","from":151.0,"location":2,"to":151.41},{"content":"很好奇這個要如何用在陶藝上呢","from":151.41,"location":2,"to":154.82},{"content":"在削的過程中這個工具會發生抖動","from":155.02,"location":2,"to":157.26},{"content":"意思關鍵就是它會來回抖動嗎","from":157.64,"location":2,"to":159.39},{"content":"是的","from":159.39,"location":2,"to":159.98},{"content":"那…","from":159.98,"location":2,"to":160.51},{"content":"是在削出波浪造型時…這麼用的","from":161.18,"location":2,"to":165.37},{"content":"不對","from":166.72,"location":2,"to":167.34},{"content":"猜錯了啊","from":167.76,"location":2,"to":168.36},{"content":"請告訴我們正確答案","from":168.45,"location":2,"to":169.8},{"content":"好的 正確答案就在各位的眼皮底下","from":169.8,"location":2,"to":172.3},{"content":"做出來就是這種感覺","from":172.3,"location":2,"to":173.26},{"content":"類似裂縫的圖案嗎","from":173.48,"location":2,"to":174.59},{"content":"是的 很細碎","from":174.59,"location":2,"to":175.24},{"content":"還能做出這種花紋… 是因為它會抖動嗎","from":175.24,"location":2,"to":178.03},{"content":"-沒錯 -也就是說…","from":178.03,"location":2,"to":179.01},{"content":"是這麼哢哢哢做出來的啊","from":179.16,"location":2,"to":180.73},{"content":"是的","from":180.73,"location":2,"to":181.1},{"content":"-有一種叫小鹿田燒的陶器\n-這裡哢哢哢地抖動 然後就會有這種花紋啊","from":181.13,"location":2,"to":184.4},{"content":"-好時髦 -在頂部觸碰到陶器的時候會反彈","from":184.41,"location":2,"to":186.6},{"content":"就會自然地產生那樣一點一點的紋樣","from":186.6,"location":2,"to":188.48},{"content":"太厲害了","from":188.48,"location":2,"to":189.16},{"content":"手就固定著不動","from":189.55,"location":2,"to":190.67},{"content":"-是的 -就會自動生成紋樣啊","from":190.67,"location":2,"to":192.34},{"content":"這是什麼","from":193.32,"location":2,"to":193.86},{"content":"這是晾衣夾吧？","from":193.86,"location":2,"to":195.27},{"content":"-是啊 晾衣夾 -這個其實並不是用來製作紋飾的 -不是嗎","from":195.27,"location":2,"to":198.49},{"content":"不是啊","from":198.49,"location":2,"to":199.2},{"content":"這個可以像這樣夾起來…","from":199.43,"location":2,"to":200.76},{"content":"但這上面寫著外卡鉗","from":200.76,"location":2,"to":203.19},{"content":"是從外面這樣支撐…","from":203.19,"location":2,"to":204.98},{"content":"是這樣嗎","from":204.98,"location":2,"to":205.47},{"content":"像這樣…","from":205.78,"location":2,"to":206.41},{"content":"我想先從它的形狀來考慮","from":207.37,"location":2,"to":209.08},{"content":"-用身體來呈現 -把這東西代入了自己","from":209.21,"location":2,"to":210.7},{"content":"這個…","from":211.2,"location":2,"to":211.92},{"content":"大致正確 只是…","from":211.92,"location":2,"to":213.55},{"content":"與其說是用來固定的 應該說是用來測量尺寸的","from":214.89,"location":2,"to":218.39},{"content":"測量尺寸用的啊","from":218.39,"location":2,"to":220.09},{"content":"-也就是說可以做好多個相同大小的作品 -是的","from":221.56,"location":2,"to":223.95},{"content":"原來如此","from":223.95,"location":2,"to":225.39},{"content":"原來是這麼用的啊","from":226.25,"location":2,"to":227.02},{"content":"在諸多工具中 我也發現了一件很讓人在意的東西","from":228.12,"location":2,"to":232.38},{"content":"那是…","from":234.05,"location":2,"to":234.7},{"content":"-小優！ -好嚇人 別拿出來啊","from":235.07,"location":2,"to":237.81},{"content":"很讓人在意嘛 這東西 簡直…","from":237.81,"location":2,"to":239.62},{"content":"而且從這裡欻的一下就戳進去了","from":239.84,"location":2,"to":241.2},{"content":"從這兩根當中歘的就戳進去了","from":242.38,"location":2,"to":244.05},{"content":"真的欸","from":244.26,"location":2,"to":245.13},{"content":"簡直就是做手術用的嘛","from":245.49,"location":2,"to":246.35},{"content":"就是手術工具嘛","from":246.35,"location":2,"to":247.78},{"content":"活脫脫的手術工具","from":247.92,"location":2,"to":248.73},{"content":"就往身體裡這樣歘的一下","from":248.73,"location":2,"to":250.32},{"content":"好痛好痛","from":250.77,"location":2,"to":251.6},{"content":"好痛…","from":251.77,"location":2,"to":252.2},{"content":"在想打耳洞的時候…","from":252.2,"location":2,"to":253.55},{"content":"打耳洞啊","from":254.26,"location":2,"to":254.81},{"content":"把友希的耳朵給哢嗒一下","from":255.28,"location":2,"to":256.77},{"content":"會開出個超大的洞啦","from":257.62,"location":2,"to":258.95},{"content":"但這是用來開洞… 是用來夾東西的？","from":260.05,"location":2,"to":261.92},{"content":"是的","from":262.19,"location":2,"to":262.9},{"content":"是夾東西用的啊？","from":263.06,"location":2,"to":264.14},{"content":"我知道了！","from":265.05,"location":2,"to":265.72},{"content":"夾剛燒製出爐的盤子","from":266.14,"location":2,"to":267.52},{"content":"不對","from":267.96,"location":2,"to":268.51},{"content":"我和你想的一樣","from":268.51,"location":2,"to":269.25},{"content":"我也是","from":269.25,"location":2,"to":269.91},{"content":"我也","from":269.91,"location":2,"to":270.31},{"content":"就是就是","from":270.31,"location":2,"to":271.18},{"content":"難道不就是嘛","from":271.39,"location":2,"to":272.12},{"content":"你們看看這裡是賣什麼的貨架","from":272.12,"location":2,"to":273.35},{"content":"上色工具…？","from":273.75,"location":2,"to":274.81},{"content":"濕噠噠的！","from":274.81,"location":2,"to":275.55},{"content":"濕噠噠？","from":276.44,"location":2,"to":277.0},{"content":"濕淋淋的…","from":277.16,"location":2,"to":278.11},{"content":"原來是這麼回事啊","from":279.29,"location":2,"to":280.35},{"content":"用來取還沒幹的東西","from":280.63,"location":2,"to":281.85},{"content":"對對","from":281.85,"location":2,"to":282.39},{"content":"取沒幹的東西嗎","from":282.39,"location":2,"to":283.17},{"content":"…很可惜","from":283.45,"location":2,"to":284.19},{"content":"-答錯了嗎 -很可惜 -不對嗎","from":284.4,"location":2,"to":286.29},{"content":"-是用它夾起盤子等等之後 -固定之後…","from":286.86,"location":2,"to":289.07},{"content":"一口氣把它放進桶裡","from":289.07,"location":2,"to":290.91},{"content":"還會有連著這個東西一起浸入釉藥的大膽操作啊","from":291.5,"location":2,"to":294.03},{"content":"原來是這樣啊","from":294.03,"location":2,"to":295.05},{"content":"-方法真是多變啊 -如果用手拿 那怎麼都會留下指紋","from":295.05,"location":2,"to":298.43},{"content":"的確","from":298.43,"location":2,"to":299.05},{"content":"-這個施釉鉗就是為了避免這種情況 -原來如此","from":299.05,"location":2,"to":302.94},{"content":"施釉鉗啊","from":302.94,"location":2,"to":304.12},{"content":"全都是些我這輩子前所未見的東西","from":305.28,"location":2,"to":307.56},{"content":"要是不製作陶藝就基本上不會接觸到這些東西","from":307.98,"location":2,"to":309.84},{"content":"-就是啊 -是啊","from":309.84,"location":2,"to":310.82},{"content":"這裡好有趣啊","from":310.96,"location":2,"to":312.08},{"content":"非